## Commit Types

- `docs:` - Documentation changes
- `fix:` - Fix doc errors
- `feat:` - New doc features
- `refactor:` - Reorganize docs
- `chore:` - Maintenance

## Safety

- Always show changes first
- Generate meaningful messages
- Don't commit secrets
- Suggest pushing, don't auto-push
